OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1781977680
OL,3,C16 year old charged with murder after
OL,4,Cteen stabbed in Dollis Hill
OL,6,FA 16 year old boy has been charged
OL,7,Fwith murder following the fatal
OL,8,Fstabbing of a teenager in north-west
OL,9,FLondon, the Metropolitan Police have
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FThe suspect, who cannot be named
OL,13,Fbecause of his age, was arrested on
OL,14,FTuesday and charged later the same day.
OL,16,FIt follows a fatal stabbing in Dudden
OL,17,FHill Lane, Dollis Hill, which officers
OL,18,Fattended at around 10.30pm on Saturday
OL,19,FMay 30.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
