PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1781977680
OL,3,C16 year old charged with murder after
OL,4,Cteen stabbed in Dollis Hill
OL,6,FJamal Ringrose, a 15 year old, was
OL,7,Ftreated at the scene for stab wounds
OL,8,Fbefore being taken to hospital, where
OL,9,Fhe died five days later.
OL,11,FDetective Chief Superintendent Luke
OL,12,FWilliams, who leads policing in the
OL,13,Farea, said on Thursday:
OL,15,F"We recognise the concern locally
OL,16,Fafter Jamal's death and want to
OL,17,Freassure our communities that we are
OL,18,Fdoing everything possible to keep
OL,19,Flocal people safe.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1781977680
OL,3,C16 year old charged with murder after
OL,4,Cteen stabbed in Dollis Hill
OL,6,F"Our officers have acted swiftly to
OL,7,Fmake arrests in connection with the
OL,8,Fwider disorder surrounding this
OL,9,Fincident.
OL,11,F"This includes putting extra powers in
OL,12,Fplace following Jamal's death,
OL,13,Fallowing our officers to stop and
OL,14,Fsearch people in the area to protect
OL,15,Fthe public and deter potential harm
OL,16,Fand criminality."
OL,18,FA further eight people were previously
OL,19,Farrested in connection with the
OL,20,Fincident, police said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@QO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
