PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1781977680
OL,3,C16 year old charged with murder after
OL,4,Cteen stabbed in Dollis Hill
OL,6,FThey include two teenage boys who were
OL,7,Fcharged with affray and possession of
OL,8,Fan offensive weapon.
OL,10,FAn 18 year old man was arrested on May
OL,11,F31 on suspicion of assault causing
OL,12,Fgrievous bodily harm, and has since
OL,13,Fbeen released on bail.
OL,15,FA 19 year old man arrested on June 4
OL,16,Fon suspicion of affray has since been
OL,17,Freleased on bail.
OL,19,FAn 18 year old man arrested on June 11
OL,20,Fon suspicion of affray and possession
OL,21,Fof drugs has since been bailed.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1781977680
OL,3,C16 year old charged with murder after
OL,4,Cteen stabbed in Dollis Hill
OL,6,FA 28 year old man was arrested on June
OL,7,F12 on suspicion of rioting and a 27-
OL,8,Fyear-old man was arrested on June 14
OL,9,Fon suspicion of the same offence. They
OL,10,Fhave both been bailed pending further
OL,11,Finquiries.
OL,13,FFinally, a 17 year old boy was
OL,14,Farrested on Monday on suspicion of
OL,15,Faffray and possession of an offensive
OL,16,Fweapon. He has also been released on
OL,17,Fbail pending further inquiries, police
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,20,FDetective Inspector Simon Ager, who is
OL,21,Fleading the investigation, said:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1781977680
OL,3,C16 year old charged with murder after
OL,4,Cteen stabbed in Dollis Hill
OL,6,F"Our thoughts continue to be with the
OL,7,Ffamily and loved ones of Jamal at a
OL,8,Fdifficult time.
OL,10,F"Our work has led to one boy being
OL,11,Fcharged with murder and we continue to
OL,12,Fwork at pace to pursue several lines
OL,13,Fof inquiry following Jamal's tragic
OL,14,Fdeath.
OL,16,F"We would like to repeat our plea to
OL,17,Fanyone with information or footage of
OL,18,Fthe incident to come forward.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
